longBusinessSummary: Chordate Medical Holding AB (publ), a medical technology company, engages in the development of products and solutions for neurostimulation treatment in Sweden. It offers Ozilia, a neuromodulation and medication-free treatment technology for chronic migraine and chronic rhinitis. The company was founded in 2005 and is based in Kista, Sweden.
